==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interscapular
<hw>In`ter*scap"u*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Between the scapul⟦ae⟧ or shoulder
blades.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to the upper back, or
the part between the shoulders; <as>as, the <ex>interscapular</ex>
feathers</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interscapulars</ent>⟦br⟧
